# False9 — Cursor Rules

This project uses the False9 multi-agent audit and completion system.
Load agent definitions from `.cursor/agents/` as custom agent instructions.

## Agents

Each agent in `.cursor/agents/` is a self-contained specialist.
Use them as system prompts or custom instructions for domain-specific code review.

## Commands

- `/f9-audit` — Deploy all agents for a full engineering audit
- `/f9-complete` — Reconstruct intent, complete unfinished work, then audit
